{"tid":126693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長期頭痛有冇巴絲知咩事","createTime":"2017-02-19T14:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T10:59:09.000Z","uid":67395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1db98c198301390987b0b3202848b159e4c8c178","tid":126693,"uid":67395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"唔知幾時開始<br />\n每日一瞓得耐小小就會開始頭痛<br />\n但呢個頭痛係間唔中<br />\n可能行兩步樓梯就會痛到仆街<br />\n但第二日一瞓醒就無事"},{"pid":"671a7a0ad56fbb2a73a3392e6e0dfe001e8d65b4","tid":126693,"uid":1494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:53:49.000Z","msg":"我最近都係咁"},{"pid":"7b07876f7c96e3e1d2ce38cef86a32de685281dd","tid":126693,"uid":67395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:32:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1c521528f47f999087620fd4dea57799ef3bb9","tid":126693,"uid":82960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:44:33.000Z","msg":"我反而係係自己睡得好臨既時候,勉強比鬧鐘嘈醒就係咁,但明明以前番學都無事,偏偏宜家係咁<br />\n樓豬訓得耐就咁,我唔肯定幫唔幫到你,我試過出戶外漫步下,照下日光就會好點. 有一排訓到黃朝八晏就頭痛"},{"pid":"5ce828c4aa8482f1b7419da7bf467d50ec81a861","tid":126693,"uid":77487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頭痛真係好辛苦<br />\n唔知係咪遺傳 老媽子都成日頭痛<br />\n成日食止痛藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f5cbdd1da844a961cfcb48e3a6f642c5592c88","tid":126693,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:08:56.000Z","msg":"去試下睇中醫針灸啊 <br />\n針完 痛小左好多好多<br />\n<br />\n我之前都間唔中頭痛<br />\n但係無食過止痛藥"},{"pid":"4121106548cc9869e9687d81b42cdce14c9f0d98","tid":126693,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4495d5c7d9b03f0f1d435cd91e79415faba372e1","tid":126693,"uid":76526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:12:39.000Z","msg":"1.頸肌肉發炎<br />\n2.枕頭問題<br />\n3.血糖低"},{"pid":"638bcdae4e78648c95f91502b90fd594647e79bb","tid":126693,"uid":57490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:14:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.頸肌肉發炎<br />\n2.枕頭問題<br />\n3.血糖低</blockquote><br />\n血糖底都會頭痛嫁？我以為淨係會頭暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8388faeb322fdb84984c6173b9e21e3edc4f4713","tid":126693,"uid":76526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:44:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1.頸肌肉發炎<br />\n2.枕頭問題<br />\n3.血糖低</blockquote><br />\n血糖底都會頭痛嫁？我以為淨係會頭暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果次我冇食野成日，個頭痛到hihi.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67164f963bac089ee48062cd7c8e89df6f004b4","tid":126693,"uid":76526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知幾時開始<br />\n每日一瞓得耐小小就會開始頭痛<br />\n但呢個頭痛係間唔中<br />\n可能行兩步樓梯就會痛到仆街<br />\n但第二日一瞓醒就無事</blockquote><br />\n我之前試過痛左一年，好可能係枕頭問題"},{"pid":"dcbc6c41de6ba6cf63967ce97448b4efcfc0807b","tid":126693,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知幾時開始<br />\n每日一瞓得耐小小就會開始頭痛<br />\n但呢個頭痛係間唔中<br />\n可能行兩步樓梯就會痛到仆街<br />\n但第二日一瞓醒就無事</blockquote><br />\n有無散光或近視<br />\n飲水量如何"},{"pid":"0e61ff5664a3fd342dee9012ebd37fc4412a396c","tid":126693,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:58:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知幾時開始<br />\n每日一瞓得耐小小就會開始頭痛<br />\n但呢個頭痛係間唔中<br />\n可能行兩步樓梯就會痛到仆街<br />\n但第二日一瞓醒就無事</blockquote><br />\n有無比白光照射到眼?"},{"pid":"68c00902576d89c442a34e15a3a19b35c7bf5a0b","tid":126693,"uid":67395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知幾時開始<br />\n每日一瞓得耐小小就會開始頭痛<br />\n但呢個頭痛係間唔中<br />\n可能行兩步樓梯就會痛到仆街<br />\n但第二日一瞓醒就無事</blockquote><br />\n有無散光或近視<br />\n飲水量如何</blockquote><br />\n乜都冇啊<br />\n一日4-5杯吧"},{"pid":"83070169321841e8559ab6f45042a220bce9b15a","tid":126693,"uid":67395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:59:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.頸肌肉發炎<br />\n2.枕頭問題<br />\n3.血糖低</blockquote><br />\n我乜都冇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9f6d498a39b20b75609f2542da386b27d19b46","tid":126693,"uid":67395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而係係自己睡得好臨既時候,勉強比鬧鐘嘈醒就係咁,但明明以前番學都無事,偏偏宜家係咁<br />\n樓豬訓得耐就咁,我唔肯定幫唔幫到你,我試過出戶外漫步下,照下日光就會好點. 有一排訓到黃朝八晏就頭痛</blockquote><br />\n頭痛真係好辛苦"},{"pid":"391c27831cd8c511019585c636d196314cd0a5ed","tid":126693,"uid":30914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:24:52.000Z","msg":"經常性痛到嘔同手震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知咩事"},{"pid":"e3701fe7791fdd91ecd0f3db2c81b80941b21857","tid":126693,"uid":9792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"我都係有時冇啦啦頭痛<br />\n又有時個心口會痛<br />\n唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9574b7888948db12d0a284ac48367b47a83b359a","tid":126693,"uid":67395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係有時冇啦啦頭痛<br />\n又有時個心口會痛<br />\n唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n心口痛可大可小喎巴打<br />\n檢查下好啲"},{"pid":"32339f4bbe1267eca8aa3755de0bf3fab5810c2a","tid":126693,"uid":67395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經常性痛到嘔同手震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知咩事</blockquote><br />\n有畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32622632ada4168e320085f3b10e762ae3dd4a0","tid":126693,"uid":78504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:55:41.000Z","msg":"我又係好易頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瞓得多會痛，小睡片刻又痛，冇食嘢都痛<br />\n有時會覺得個頭入面有條血管好似跳得好快咁，跳一下就痛一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2aa3222b14793d7be498f3cc044e8569d598d2","tid":126693,"uid":2025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知幾時開始<br />\n每日一瞓得耐小小就會開始頭痛<br />\n但呢個頭痛係間唔中<br />\n可能行兩步樓梯就會痛到仆街<br />\n但第二日一瞓醒就無事</blockquote><br />\n有無比白光照射到眼?</blockquote><br />\n日光射到眼都關事？？<br />\n我通常星期六日先黎頭痛<br />\n自問又工作壓力又唔算大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b0e825b9d90acbe1ef82c49583f9df2d7c0626","tid":126693,"uid":2462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:01:34.000Z","msg":"間唔中都會冇端端頭痛<br />\n訓得少又痛 戴得con多又會痛<br />\n行行下街/訓訓下教醒左都會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過睇完中醫情況改善左不少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都會痛 但冇咁密同埋冇咁痛"},{"pid":"1b6a09690632da3f6d9ceb5e4fdadd59054eaf27","tid":126693,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T23:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔知幾時開始<br />\n每日一瞓得耐小小就會開始頭痛<br />\n但呢個頭痛係間唔中<br />\n可能行兩步樓梯就會痛到仆街<br />\n但第二日一瞓醒就無事</blockquote><br />\n有無比白光照射到眼?</blockquote><br />\n日光射到眼都關事？？<br />\n我通常星期六日先黎頭痛<br />\n自問又工作壓力又唔算大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果有散光<br />\n比強光照到係會有頭痛<br />\n通常會由眼球開始痛<br />\n會痛兩致三日<br />\n我就係咁<br />\n師兄可以去驗一驗眼<br />\n<br />\n另外血糖低，脱水都會<br />\n<br />\n飯葡萄糖水，或黑糖可減低頭痛時既痛楚<br />\n我有段時間又係成日痛<br />\n唔知咩事，睇西醫淨係比止痛藥<br />\n<br />\n情況有兩三年，之後少左"},{"pid":"e3ba1044b1430e32ee1196a4fc6eb9607c2320f7","tid":126693,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T23:29:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔知幾時開始<br />\n每日一瞓得耐小小就會開始頭痛<br />\n但呢個頭痛係間唔中<br />\n可能行兩步樓梯就會痛到仆街<br />\n但第二日一瞓醒就無事</blockquote><br />\n有無比白光照射到眼?</blockquote><br />\n日光射到眼都關事？？<br />\n我通常星期六日先黎頭痛<br />\n自問又工作壓力又唔算大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係房暗既時候<br />\n對住個mon <br />\n都會引發頭痛"}]}